data.description: Great opportunity!  3.75 Assumable loan.  Payoff amount is $370,068.22. You'll fall in love with this almost new home. It has a lot of natural light and it has 9 ft vaulted ceilings with nice lamps. It has a very spacious primary bedroom with a five piece bathroom and walk-in closet. It is an amazing open concept with a spacious kitchen with granite counters, the living room has a walk out to the big backyard. The backyard has enough space to park your RV or Boat and create your own garden. It has solar panels to save a lot on Electricity. It is only 3 minutes from the nice shops, restaurants and Walmart. It is close to school too. It is very well kept with lots of love and care. Come to see the breathtaking views from the front porch.
